data.description: Presenting a spacious triplex located on a generous lot, this property offers an excellent investment opportunity. The triplex comprises two 2-bedroom units and one 1-bedroom unit, catering to various tenant preferences. The top-floor owner's unit is a standout, featuring vaulted ceilings, exposed beams with tongue and groove accents, a beautifully remodeled kitchen, brand new carpets,, in-unit washer/dryer, 2 bedrooms, a full bath, a family room, and a cupola that adds a unique touch. Units 1 and 2 conveniently share a washer/dryer. Over the years, the property has received numerous cosmetic updates including paint, new flooring, bathroom renovation, kitchen upgrades, and exterior stairs. Its location offers great potential for long-term tenants or furnished short-term rentals, given its proximity to the UMED district and JBER. Whether you seek steady rental income or flexible leasing options, this triplex is a promising investment opportunity.
